{"tid":1036991,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【小學生齊打交？】港獨「小學雞」內鬨鬧劇！何俊謙被「同路人」公開手機號碼","createTime":"2019-02-25T15:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T18:57:44.000Z","uid":2748,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9067282fbf1add524cd4a79cf4f94dd26bd2a861","tid":1036991,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.speakout.hk/articles/cover/20190224/506b6e7f8ddc4698d03cc04c2213b60d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.speakout.hk%2Farticles%2Fcover%2F20190224%2F506b6e7f8ddc4698d03cc04c2213b60d.jpg&h=5c4a39e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n﻿曾公開指片「呼籲各位針對中國人」的港獨分子何俊謙，日前被人在社交網站公開其手機號碼後被人致電騷擾，其後何聲稱是馬鞍山「獨派」區議員陳國強下屬、社區主任邱文勁所為。<br />\n<br />\n二人在網上隨空駁火。何更向陳國強聲討為不得要領，事件變成一場可笑的港獨「小學雞」內鬨鬧劇。"},{"pid":"cefc3b50047abb941ed9a66d6ba3467176c4aa67","tid":1036991,"uid":2748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1f97f30c8579a3ebcad8df3e0f1b22620e417a","tid":1036991,"uid":2748,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7399c6cf2d3af4bde50fabb2336fa7719feeb8b","tid":1036991,"uid":226955,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:13:15.000Z","msg":"港人講地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪嚟錯咗香討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cb79212194d4cb9a71ddc450665d2ab2be1683","tid":1036991,"uid":1435,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:14:52.000Z","msg":"港人講地就咪撚貼出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65843f0fb9269a5a716700d60b801a689b432fca","tid":1036991,"uid":2748,"like":1,"dislike":